


				 l u c i l l e

			  Global Illumination Renderer


 features:
	- Monte Carlo ray tracing
	- Photon mapping
	- Supports RIB( The RenderMan(R) Interface Bytestream ) file format
	- RenderMan Shading Language( limited and experimental )
	- Parallel Rendering( with MPI )
	- SIMD(x86 SSE, G4 AltiVec) optimized ray tracing

 supported platform:
	- Mac OS-X
	- Linux( x86 )
	- Windows
	

